<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">三　長老之譬喻二</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第九　提蜜羅普毘耶品</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">九〇　鉢頭磨普毘耶（蓮花）</cb:mulu><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.132" type="PTS_hide"></ref><cb:div type="other">
<milestone unit="juan" n="10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第十　須陀品</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.133"></ref>第十　須陀品</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">九一　須陀頻第耶（漆食塊）</cb:mulu><head>九一　須陀頻第耶（漆食塊）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0175a1201">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0175a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>跳越障礙墻，渡過憂悲海，彼佛值供養，及其弟子等。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0175a1301">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0175a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>供養斯人等，涅槃無畏者，布施得大福，誰亦不能量。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0175a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0175a1401">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0175a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>假令四大洲，統主挑戰鬥，不值斯供養，十六分之一。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0176a" n="0176a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0176a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0176a0101">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0176a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>人中之勝者，悉達多佛陀；支提崩壞處，修復為供養，
<lb ed="N" n="0176a02"/>更以清淨心，吾施以漆喰。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0176a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0176a0301">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0176a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>依時所作業，九十四劫間，吾不知惡趣，修復此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0176a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0176a0401">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0176a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>三十劫之昔，名稱作修復<note n="0176001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Paṭisaṅkhāra（修復）。</note>，七寶十三人，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0176a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0176a0501">七</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0176a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0176a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0176a0601" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者須陀頻第耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0176a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0176a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0176a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0176a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0176a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">九二　須欽提陀（善考）</cb:mulu><head>九二　須欽提陀（善考）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0176a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0176a1201">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0176a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>救主帝沙佛，吾嘗施座椅，佛出於日種，雀躍心歡喜。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0176a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0176a1301">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0176a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>三十八劫昔，做大滿足王<note n="0176001-1" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Mahāruci（大滿足）。</note>，其富甚宏大，亦有多座褥。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0176a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0176a1401">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0176a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>更以清淨心，布施佛座椅，嘗自積善業，自享己業果。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0177a" n="0177a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0177a0101"><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.134"></ref>四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0177a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>彼時施椅子，九十二劫間，吾不知惡趣，施椅此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0177a0201">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0177a0201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>三十八劫昔，轉輪王三人，滿足近滿足<note n="0177002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Ruci（滿足）。</note><note n="0177003" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Uparuci（近滿足）。</note>，言稱大滿足。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0177a0301">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0177a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0177a0401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者斯欽提陀長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">九三　阿達佉拉迦（折半衣）</cb:mulu><head>九三　阿達佉拉迦（折半衣）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0177a1201">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0177a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾達最悲心<note n="0177001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 Paramakāruññapatto（異本）。</note>，身為惡臭纏，於帝沙尊佛，吾施折半布。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0177a1301">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0177a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>既施折半布，於天一劫樂，其餘幾數劫，善業吾成就。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0177a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0177a1401">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0177a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>彼時行布施，九十二劫間，吾不知惡趣，施布此果報。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0178a" n="0178a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0178a0101">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0178a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四十九劫昔，轉輪王示現，人王三十二，其名為乳糜<note n="0178002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">odana（乳麋）。</note>。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0178a0201">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0178a0201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0178a0301" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者阿達佉拉迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">九四　斯質多耶迦（針布施）</cb:mulu><head>九四　斯質多耶迦（針布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0178a1001">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0178a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>最上親惠城<note n="0178001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Bandhumā 正寫為 Bandhumatī（親惠城）。</note>，吾昔職鐵工，毘婆尸大仙，吾行針布施。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0178a1101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0178a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>如斯善業故，智慧比金剛，解脫無貪欲，達至諸漏盡。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0178a1201"><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.135"></ref>三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0178a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>既已過去世，乃至未來世，吾以智慧識，施針此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0178a1301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0178a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>九十一劫昔，金剛似七人<note n="0178002-1" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Vajirasama（金剛似）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0178a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0178a1401">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0178a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0179a" n="0179a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0179a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0179a0101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者斯質多耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0179a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0179a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0179a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0179a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0179a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0179a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">九五　康達瑪利耶（香華鬘）</cb:mulu><head>九五　康達瑪利耶（香華鬘）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0179a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0179a0801">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0179a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>覆以素馨花，適於佛香塔，為佛悉達多，吾建香塔婆。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0179a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0179a0901">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0179a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>姿容值黃金，世間大導師，光輝如睡蓮，盛燃如祭火。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0179a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0179a1001">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0179a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>壯如虎牡牛，生尊猛獅子，比丘眾隨坐，沙門之勝者，
<lb ed="N" n="0179a11"/>吾禮敬其足，指向北方去。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0179a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0179a1201">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0179a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>由施香華鬘，九十四劫間，吾應可成佛，為果故至明，
<lb ed="N" n="0179a13"/>惡趣吾不知，供養佛果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0179a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0179a1401">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0179a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>三十九劫昔，有十六人王，稱名為天香<note n="0179001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Devagandha（天香）。</note>，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0180a" n="0180a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0180a0101">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0180a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0180a0201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者康達瑪利耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">九六　提普毘耶（三花）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.136"></ref>九六　提普毘耶（三花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0180a0801">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0180a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾住於森林，往昔為獵人，吾見波吒釐<note n="0180001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">波吒釐（Pāṭalī）樹為毘婆尸佛之菩提樹。</note>，覆撒三瓣花。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0180a0901">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0180a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>其時七落葉，向外吾擲去，內外身清淨，無漏心解脫。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0180a1001">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0180a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>世間之導師，正覺毘婆尸，禮拜波吒釐，當場即息絕。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0180a1101">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0180a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>供養供養樹，九十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，供樹此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0180a1201">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0180a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>三十三劫昔，一切處愉悅<note n="0180002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Samantapāsādika（一切處愉悅）。</note>，大力十三人，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0180a1301">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0180a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0180a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0180a1401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者提普毘耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0181a" n="0181a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">九七　瑪多頻底迦（蜜塊）</cb:mulu><head>九七　瑪多頻底迦（蜜塊）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0181a0701">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0181a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾見深林中，音靜不搖動，悉達多佛陀，接受尊供物。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0181a0801">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0181a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>恰如大象鎮，及壯牛駿馬，亦如月光輝，諸神皈敬彼，
<lb ed="N" n="0181a09"/>爾時吾心喜，智慧湧出生。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0181a1001">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0181a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>佛由禪定起，施蜜於尊師，禮敬尊師足，指向東方去。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0181a1101"><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.137"></ref>四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0181a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>三十四劫昔，須陀蘇那王，爾時蜜由蓮，由吾食流出，
<lb ed="N" n="0181a12"/>蜜雨從空降，嘗為此業報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0181a1301">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0181a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>彼時布施蜜，九十四劫間，惡趣吾不知，施蜜此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0181a1401">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0181a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>三十四劫昔，王者有四人，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0182a" n="0182a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0182a0101">七</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0182a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0182a0201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者瑪多頻底迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">九八　勢那薩那達耶迦（坐臥具布施）</cb:mulu><head>九八　勢那薩那達耶迦（坐臥具布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0182a0501">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0182a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>悉達多佛尊，吾施樹葉蓆，四徧為奉事，撒庫斯瑪花。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0182a0601">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0182a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>如宮殿樂洞，享豪華物樂，高貴鮮花朶，雨花落臥牀<note n="0182001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 sayane' bhivassanti（暹羅本）。</note>。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0182a0701">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0182a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>幾朶美花敷，散落吾臥牀，爾時牀舖上，雨花紛紛降。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0182a0801">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0182a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾施樹葉蓆，九十四劫間，惡趣吾不知，施蓆此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0182a0901">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0182a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>第五劫往昔，名稱堅固蓆<note n="0182002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 Thitāsanthāraka（堅固蓆）（暹羅本）。</note>，人王有七人，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0182a1001"><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.138"></ref>六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0182a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0182a1101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者塞那薩那達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0183a" n="0183a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">九九　威耶瓦奢迦（奉事）</cb:mulu><head>九九　威耶瓦奢迦（奉事）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0183a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0183a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>毘婆尸佛陀，復有數多眾，吾時為使役，盡奉諸所用。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0183a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0183a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>善逝大仙尊，吾無布施物，謹以清淨心，吾禮尊師足。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0183a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0183a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>彼時為奉事，九十一劫間，吾不知惡趣，奉事此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0183a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0183a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>第八劫往昔，名稱善考王<note n="0183001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Sucintita（善考）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0183a0701">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0183a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0183a0801" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者威耶瓦奢迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0184a" n="0184a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一〇〇　弗多帕他迦（奉事佛）</cb:mulu><head>一〇〇　弗多帕他迦（奉事佛）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0184a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0184a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>毘婆尸佛前，吾吹螺貝者，善逝大仙傍，吾盡執奉事。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0184a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0184a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>世間之救主，果報盡奉事，七萬種樂器，常此圍繞吾。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0184a0501"><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.139"></ref>三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0184a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>大仙吾奉事，九十一劫間，吾不知惡趣，奉事此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0184a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0184a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>九十四劫昔，其名稱大響<note n="0184001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Mahānigghosa（大響）。</note>，大力十六人，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0184a0701">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0184a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0184a0801" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者弗多帕他迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0184a1201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">攝頌：</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a13"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgN29p0184a1301" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:3em">須陀頻達、彼佉拉<note n="0184001-1" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">此前之 Sucintita 略去。</note>，<note n="0184002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Kammāra（鐵工）Sūcidāyaka 嘗為鐵工匠，故作斯言。</note>堪瑪拉與甘達瑪、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0184a14"/><l style="text-indent:3em">提普庇耶與瑪多、勢那與威耶瓦奢、</l>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0185a" n="0185a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a01"/><l style="text-indent:3em">丹瑪迦末共十人<note n="0185003" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Dhammaka（法）。指 Buddhūpaṭṭhāka 長老。</note>，偈整七十此品宣。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0185a0701" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">十品攝頌：</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a08"/><lg xml:id="lgN29p0185a0801" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:3em">開始佛陀品第一、西哈薩那、須菩提、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a09"/><l style="text-indent:3em">軍頭波漠、優波離、維伽尼與薩伽質塔尼耶、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a10"/><l style="text-indent:3em">那伽薩瑪羅、提蜜羅、第十須陀品，</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a11"/><l style="text-indent:3em">共偈一千四百首，更有五十有五偈。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0185a1201" style="margin-left:22em">佛陀品十組</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0185a1301" style="margin-left:22em">第一之百人終</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0185a14"/>
</cb:div></body></text></TEI>